NaSchSim - Simple Freeway Traffic Simulator based on Nagel Schreckenberg model. 
Coded in Python using PyGlet and OpenGL. 
Inspired by Stausim by Bastinat0r.

Setup:
    Requires PyGlet (easy_install pyglet)

Run:
    python main.py

Colors:
    Green - Accelerating Car
    Blue - Car driving at max. speed
    Yellow - Car driving with reduced speed.
    Red - Car hitting the breaks.

